    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>A Goblin Warrior is a hit-and-run fighter driven from deep mountain caves by some unknown force pressing southwest. Crude spear, quick legs, zero hesitation -- it drops in, stabs, and runs back up the cliff before you can answer.</p>",
      "director": "<p>Warriors open with Spear Charge for mobile hit-and-run from the cliff walls, retreating back to elevation after each strike. Bury the Point is their pressure tool against durable targets -- bleeding (save ends) drains action economy. Keep them shifting and never static. They work best when Runners tie up attention and Warriors flank freely.</p>",
